,"r04s7s",{"d":"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z"}],"$undefined"]}]}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-sm font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mb-2","children":"Find the Right Tool"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-xs text-[#8BA3BE] mb-4","children":"Browse 79+ enterprise software reviews"}],["$","$L12",null,{"href":"/","className":"inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-4 py-2 bg-[#3B82F6] hover:bg-[#2563EB] text-white text-xs font-bold rounded-lg transition-colors","children":["Browse Tools ",["$","svg",null,{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-3 h-3","children":[["$","path","1ays0h",{"d":"M5 12h14"}],["$","path","xquz4c",{"d":"m12 5 7 7-7 7"}],"$undefined"]}]]}]]}]]}]}]
1a:["$","h3","24",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-8 mb-3","children":"GDPR Compliance"}]
1b:["$","p","25",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["For companies handling EU customer data, GDPR compliance is mandatory. Key requirements: data processing records, consent management, Data Protection Officer appointment, 72-hour breach notification, and Data Processing Agreements with subprocessors."]}]
1c:["$","h2","27",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"Security Monitoring"}]
1d:["$","p","29",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Cloudflare"}],": Protects against DDoS attacks, provides WAF (Web Application Firewall), and secures API endpoints with rate limiting and bot management. Cloudflare's Zero Trust platform replaces traditional VPNs."]}]
1e:["$","p","30",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"CrowdStrike"}],": Endpoint detection and response (EDR) that monitors all devices for suspicious activity. Its Falcon platform uses AI to detect and respond to threats in real-time."]}]
1f:["$","p","31",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Snyk"}],": Developer security platform that scans code, dependencies, containers, and infrastructure as code for vulnerabilities. Integrates directly into CI/CD pipelines."]}]
20:["$","h2","33",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"Employee Security Training"}]
21:["$","p","35",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Humans remain the weakest link. Implement mandatory security training covering: phishing identification, password hygiene, safe browsing practices, and incident reporting procedures. Regular phishing simulations help build awareness."]}]
22:["$","h2","37",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"Incident Response Plan"}]
23:["$","p","39",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Every SaaS company needs a documented incident response plan with defined roles (incident commander, communications lead, engineering response), communication templates for customers and regulators, and a post-mortem process."]}]
24:["$","h2","41",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"The Minimum Security Stack"}]
25:["$","p","43",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["For a growing SaaS company, the minimum viable security stack is: Okta (identity + SSO + MFA) + Cloudflare (WAF + DDoS) + Snyk (code scanning) + a password manager (1Password or Bitwarden) + CrowdStrike or SentinelOne (endpoint protection). Budget approximately 8-12% of engineering budget for security tools and personnel."]}]
